As a user I must be able to edit my username
As a user I must be able to edit my firstname & lastname
As a user I must be able to edit my location
As a user I must be able to edit my date of birth
As a user I must be able to edit my address
As a user I must be able to edit my job title
As a user I must be able to edit my profile picture
As a user I must be able to save my edits in one click: this will then redirect me to the “read view”
